DOE algorithms options
======================

A simple way to solve an :class:`.OptimizationProblem` is to use the API method
:meth:`~gemseo.api.execute_algo`. E.g.

.. code::

	from gemseo.api import execute_algo
	from gemseo.problems.analytical.rosenbrock import Rosenbrock

	problem = Rosenbrock()
	sol = execute_algo(problem, "OT_LHS", n_samples=20)

They are also used in all MDO and DOE scenarios in the dictionary
passed to the :meth:`.MDODiscipline.execute` method.

